  {
    "id": "f_csv_b8354c20f5",
    "slug": "when-i-was-in-the-first-grade-i-was-afraid-of-the-teacher-and-had-a-miserable-ti",
    "texto": "When I was in the first grade I was afraid of the teacher and had a miserable time in the reading circle, a difficulty that was overcome by the loving patience of my second grade teacher. Even though I could read, I refused to do so.",
